g\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><h3>Malibu Valley<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">M<\/span>alibu Valley presents a remarkable opportunity to own an estate property on the edge of one of the world\u2019s most vibrant cities.<\/p>\n<p>A private gated enclave of 26 homes situated on 100 acres nestled within the Santa Monica Mountains, Malibu Valley includes new construction homes available for purchase. Homes range from 6,000 to 11,000 square feet, each with its own architectural style. No expense is spared, with each home\u2019s individualized designer touches, including imported marble, hand painted tiles, luxury appliances, handcrafted finishes and Crestron automation.<\/p>\n<p>Malibu Valley also offers the rare opportunity to purchase a Lot and design your own dream home. Extraordinary approvals allow for 50-foot height limits, increased wall and fence heights and almost limitless design freedom.<\/p>\n<h3>Climate<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">O<\/span>nly 3% of the world has a Mediterranean Climate, characterized by dry summers and mild winters. And even in those few places, there are limited opportunities where you can surf and ski in the same day, be in close proximity to boating and off-roading and mountain biking or horseback riding on hundreds of miles of trails. Imagine having breakfast on a snow-covered mountain, lunch in a desert oasis and dinner on the beach while watching the sunset in one jaw-dropping day. Malibu Valley is that one spectacular place \u2013 your home base to explore and experience everything Southern California has to offer.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div><div class=\"flex_column av_one_fifth  av-hide-on-mobile  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-6  el_after_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-last  right-third \" style='background: #ffffff; border-width:1px; border-color:#ffffff; border-style:solid; padding:12px; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:2px; '><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"exce